name: Moana Style
description:
This is a DreamArtist Textual Inversion Style Embedding trained on a beautiful AI image (my own) of a tropical South Pacific island beach. You can get stunning ocean waves, beach and palm tree effects in your images by calling Style-Moana in the positive prompt, and if you want to temper the effect, also call Style-Moana-neg in the negative prompt.

If you'd like the effect to come through stronger (some models need it), try bumping up the emphasis on Style-Moana - see the images below.

Please consider joining my Patreon! Advanced SD tutorials, settings explanations, adult-art, from a female content creator (me!) patreon.com/theally
